reviewText: my daughter is fan of this show
Great little movie for my 5-year old little girl.
i love anything that got to do with mermaids someone else feeling might be different...they are beautiful creatures and i believe they exist.
My daughter loves this movie...we've watched it numerous times already!!

My daughter heard about this series threw her cousins.  I bought these on a whim not knowing if she would like them or not.  So I spent the money.  She watched it one time and she fell in for the series.  She has watched it for the fourth time now going on her 5th time around.  The show has a lot of humor and just a whole lot of mermaid adventures.  It is a very wholesome show which I have viewed some of it with my daughter.  I would recommend the series for any young girl who likes to swim and likes a bit of the magical fantasy.
This is a cute movie for my daughter who loves mermaids.  Wish that the show was still on, she loves it.
